description:
Sen. Tommy Tuberville (or "Coach," as he asks C&B to call him) phones in to discuss the Marxist left's war on the American family and refusal to listen to what the American people said on Election Day as they push more spending, more debt, more inflation. Southern states are beating covid, as NYT's Charles Blow sees on the map. Fauci has failed, and Sen. Paul demands he resign. OSHA guidelines push employers to vaccinate.
